## 🔧 Step-by-Step Implementation

1. **Setup & Scripts**: [deploy.sh](file:///c:/Users/Dell/ANTIGRAVITY_CODE/AWS/vscode-web-ide/deploy.sh) for Swap + Alpine Docker + Base Nginx.
2. **Backend Architecture**: Establish the `SessionManager` class to orchestrate Docker containers and port mappings.
3. **Frontend Integration**: Send `sessionId` headers with every request and WebSocket connection.
4. **AI & UI Polish**: Build the Bedrock prompt injection system.

We are implementing exactly this structure.
